{
  "stem": "9730.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So since our medics, you know, took them to that field hospital I had seen the day before, I-- I knew that I wanted to go back there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But because this was May 7th and the next day was the official end of the war, I-- I was really too busy with theses masses of surrendering German troops to get away.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it took me a few days to get back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I did get back, I wanted to know, of course, how they were all doing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I especially remember this woman that had left this impression on my mind, and-- and I wanted to find her.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I finally did find her bunk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I learned that she had collapsed once she was admitted to the hospital and was now listed in critical condition.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she was still quite lucid, and we had a talk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from that time on, I simply needed to find out more about her and how she would fare.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I made it my business to visit all of them, but all this gravitated towards this one young woman, and saw her through a real crisis yet at a later date.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And eventually, she did improve.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the more we talked and the more we found out about each other, we-- we were struck by the similarity of backgrounds and found the many things that we liked about each other, the similar, but also that we liked-- had similar likes and dislikes.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And out of that grew the relationship which led to our marriage a year later in Paris.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name at that time was Gerda Weissmann.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them had already died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of them were to die in days to come.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
